snippet.title: Piano in VR - The Entertainer by Scott Joplin on a virtual piano
snippet.description:
This video is a recorded demo version of VRPianist app, developed by me :) (= a solo indie developer/student Tereza Preislerová). In this VR game, you can play on the virtual piano according to the visual instructions. You don't need to be a piano player at all. It's my first game and is still in development and will be released to public in May 2021. I would love to hear some feedback, if you have any questions or suggestions :)

You can find more information about this project here:
https://vrpianist.com
https://www.facebook.com/VRPianist

Thank you for watching and have a nice day!
